    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A vegetable juice, red in its natural state, used in the Middle Ages as a coloring; probably obtained from the turnsole plant.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
